{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon, Original Serialized Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-06",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/maltesefalcon_2511_librivox/maltesefalcon_06_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Chapter 6 - The Undersized Shadow",
  "reader_name": "Mark Nelson",
  "page_num": 3,
  "page_total": 5,
  "page_start_sec": 496.1,
  "page_end_sec": 736.5,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.735,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 496.1,
      "end": 498.68,
      "text": "There was a long pause before she asked uneasily,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 499.56,
      "end": 500.16,
      "text": "You...",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 500.58,
      "end": 501.16,
      "text": "you know him?"
    },
    {
      "start": 502.6,
      "end": 503.58,
      "text": "I saw him to-night.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 504.832,
      "end": 507.22,
      "text": "Spade maintained his light conversational manner",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 507.36,
      "end": 508.96,
      "text": "and did not look up from his feet."
    },
    {
      "start": 510.18,
      "end": 512.4,
      "text": "He was going into the giri to see George Arliss.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 513.92,
      "end": 515.62,
      "text": "You mean you saw him to talk to?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 516.736,
      "end": 519.1,
      "text": "Only for a few minutes till the performance started.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 520.82,
      "end": 522.92,
      "text": "She got up from the settee and went to the fireplace",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 523.12,
      "end": 524.16,
      "text": "to poke at the fire."
    },
    {
      "start": 525.28,
      "end": 526.86,
      "text": "Then she changed slightly the position",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 526.86,
      "end": 528.46,
      "text": "of an ornament on the mantelpiece,"
    },
    {
      "start": 529.08,
      "end": 532.04,
      "text": "crossed the room to get a box of cigarettes from a table in a corner,"
    },
    {
      "start": 532.64,
      "end": 533.42,
      "text": "straightened a curtain,"
    },
    {
      "start": 533.54,
      "end": 534.76,
      "text": "and returned to her seat."
    },
    {
      "start": 535.78,
      "end": 537.82,
      "text": "Her face was now smooth and unworried.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 539.2,
      "end": 541.26,
      "text": "Spade grinned sideways at her and said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 542.208,
      "end": 542.66,
      "text": "You're good.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 542.88,
      "end": 544.24,
      "text": "You're very good."
    },
    {
      "start": 545.04,
      "end": 547.0,
      "text": "Her face didn't change.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 547.94,
      "end": 548.82,
      "text": "She asked quietly,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 549.94,
      "end": 550.74,
      "text": "What did he say?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 552.096,
      "end": 552.54,
      "text": "About what?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 553.9,
      "end": 554.62,
      "text": "She hesitated.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 555.904,
      "end": 556.34,
      "text": "About me?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 557.02,
      "end": 557.72,
      "text": "Nothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 559.072,
      "end": 561.7,
      "text": "Spade turned to hold his lighter under the end of her cigarette.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 562.18,
      "end": 565.04,
      "text": "His eyes were shiny in a wooden Satan's face."
    },
    {
      "start": 566.46,
      "end": 566.96,
      "text": "Well,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 567.1,
      "end": 568.06,
      "text": "what did he say?"
    },
    {
      "start": 568.84,
      "end": 570.94,
      "text": "She asked with half-playful petulance.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 572.32,
      "end": 575.36,
      "text": "He offered me five thousand dollars for the black bird.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 576.82,
      "end": 577.32,
      "text": "She jumped,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 577.48,
      "end": 579.14,
      "text": "her teeth tore the end of his cigarette,"
    },
    {
      "start": 579.36,
      "end": 580.26,
      "text": "and her eyes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 580.44,
      "end": 581.26,
      "text": "after a swift,"
    },
    {
      "start": 581.38,
      "end": 582.66,
      "text": "alarmed glance at Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 582.76,
      "end": 583.7,
      "text": "turned away from him."
    },
    {
      "start": 585.24,
      "end": 586.94,
      "text": "\"'You're not going to poke at the fire and",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 586.94,
      "end": 588.26,
      "text": "go around straightening the room again,"
    },
    {
      "start": 588.34,
      "end": 588.76,
      "text": "are you?'"
    },
    {
      "start": 589.14,
      "end": 590.36,
      "text": "he asked lazily."
    },
    {
      "start": 591.44,
      "end": 592.32,
      "text": "She laughed a clear,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 592.38,
      "end": 593.06,
      "text": "girlish laugh,"
    },
    {
      "start": 593.6,
      "end": 595.2,
      "text": "dropped the mangled cigarette into a tray,"
    },
    {
      "start": 595.38,
      "end": 596.86,
      "text": "and looked at him with clear,"
    },
    {
      "start": 596.96,
      "end": 597.72,
      "text": "merry eyes."
    },
    {
      "start": 599.3,
      "end": 600.56,
      "text": "\"'I won't,' she promised.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 601.58,
      "end": 602.56,
      "text": "\"'And what did you say?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 603.872,
      "end": 606.13,
      "text": "\"'Five thousand is a lot of money.' She",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 606.66,
      "end": 608.78,
      "text": "smiled as if she thought he was jesting."
    },
    {
      "start": 609.46,
      "end": 609.78,
      "text": "But when,"
    },
    {
      "start": 610.0,
      "end": 610.96,
      "text": "instead of smiling,"
    },
    {
      "start": 611.16,
      "end": 612.4,
      "text": "he looked gravely at her,"
    },
    {
      "start": 612.9,
      "end": 614.12,
      "text": "her smile became confused,"
    },
    {
      "start": 614.56,
      "end": 614.98,
      "text": "faint,"
    },
    {
      "start": 615.14,
      "end": 616.44,
      "text": "and presently vanished."
    },
    {
      "start": 617.7,
      "end": 619.04,
      "text": "In its place came a hurt,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 619.14,
      "end": 619.9,
      "text": "bewildered look."
    },
    {
      "start": 621.472,
      "end": 624.02,
      "text": "\"'Surely you're not really considering it,' she said.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 624.84,
      "end": 625.2,
      "text": "\"'Why not?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 625.45,
      "end": 627.8,
      "text": "Five thousand is a lot of money.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 628.32,
      "end": 628.96,
      "text": "\"'But,"
    },
    {
      "start": 628.96,
      "end": 629.14,
      "text": "Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 629.26,
      "end": 629.6,
      "text": "Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 630.14,
      "end": 631.44,
      "text": "you promised to help me.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 632.4,
      "end": 633.64,
      "text": "Her hands were on his arm.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 634.46,
      "end": 635.26,
      "text": "\"'I trusted you.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 635.46,
      "end": 636.48,
      "text": "You can't—'"
    },
    {
      "start": 636.5,
      "end": 636.736,
      "text": "it?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 637.5,
      "end": 638.24,
      "text": "She broke off,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 638.34,
      "end": 640.6,
      "text": "took her hands from his sleeve and worked them together."
    },
    {
      "start": 641.824,
      "end": 644.14,
      "text": "Spade smiled gently into her troubled eyes.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 645.312,
      "end": 648.12,
      "text": "\"'Don't let's try to figure out how much you've trusted me,'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 648.64,
      "end": 649.0,
      "text": "he said."
    },
    {
      "start": 649.84,
      "end": 650.96,
      "text": "\"'I promised to help you,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 651.04,
      "end": 653.68,
      "text": "but you didn't tell me anything about a black bird.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 655.264,
      "end": 656.28,
      "text": "\"'But you must have known,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 657.05,
      "end": 659.12,
      "text": "or—or you wouldn't have told me about it.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 659.84,
      "end": 660.68,
      "text": "You do know now."
    },
    {
      "start": 661.06,
      "end": 661.66,
      "text": "You"
    },
    {
      "start": 661.9,
      "end": 664.08,
      "text": "won't—you can't treat me that way.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 665.12,
      "end": 666.76,
      "text": "eyes were cobalt-blue prayers.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 668.16,
      "end": 670.78,
      "text": "\"'Five thousand,' he said for the third time,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 671.28,
      "end": 672.31,
      "text": "\"'is a lot of money.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 673.48,
      "end": 675.06,
      "text": "She lifted her shoulders and hands",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 675.06,
      "end": 676.74,
      "text": "and let them fall in a gesture that"
    },
    {
      "start": 676.84,
      "end": 677.54,
      "text": "accepted defeat."
    },
    {
      "start": 678.82,
      "end": 681.68,
      "text": "\"'It is,' she agreed in a small dull voice.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 682.7,
      "end": 684.78,
      "text": "\"'It is far more than I could ever offer you,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 684.89,
      "end": 686.48,
      "text": "if I must bid for your"
    },
    {
      "start": 686.58,
      "end": 687.168,
      "text": "loyalty.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 688.416,
      "end": 689.12,
      "text": "Spade laughed.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 689.64,
      "end": 691.78,
      "text": "His laughter was brief and somewhat bitter."
    },
    {
      "start": 692.56,
      "end": 694.44,
      "text": "\"'That is good,' he said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 694.56,
      "end": 695.36,
      "text": "coming from you."
    },
    {
      "start": 696.34,
      "end": 698.01,
      "text": "\"'What have you given me besides money?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 699.16,
      "end": 700.8,
      "text": "\"'Have you given me any of your confidence,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 701.1,
      "end": 702.22,
      "text": "any of the truth,"
    },
    {
      "start": 702.9,
      "end": 704.08,
      "text": "\"'any help in helping you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 704.832,
      "end": 708.08,
      "text": "\"'Haven't you tried to buy my loyalty with money and nothing else?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 708.72,
      "end": 709.06,
      "text": "\"'Well,"
    },
    {
      "start": 709.22,
      "end": 710.34,
      "text": "if I'm peddling it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 710.66,
      "end": 712.7,
      "text": "why shouldn't I let it go to the highest bidder?'"
    },
    {
      "start": 714.34,
      "end": 716.31,
      "text": "\"'I've given you all the money I have.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 717.376,
      "end": 719.16,
      "text": "Tears glistened in her white-ringed eyes.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 719.4,
      "end": 721.32,
      "text": "Her voice was hoarse,"
    },
    {
      "start": 721.48,
      "end": 721.9,
      "text": "vibrant."
    },
    {
      "start": 723.3,
      "end": 724.82,
      "text": "\"'I've thrown myself on your mercy.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 725.38,
      "end": 726.82,
      "text": "Told you that without your help."
    },
    {
      "start": 727.14,
      "end": 727.96,
      "text": "I'm utterly lost."
    },
    {
      "start": 728.88,
      "end": 729.96,
      "text": "What else is there?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 731.04,
      "end": 734.24,
      "text": "She suddenly moved close to him on the settee and cried angrily.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 735.18,
      "end": 736.5,
      "text": "\"'Can I buy you with my body?'",
      "para_break": true
    }
  ]
}